{"tid":914191,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濾水器邊隻好？","createTime":"2018-11-24T05:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T17:27:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7ee60067e198c45a88eef7f2abf4fc72f8e067","tid":914191,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事緣見到哩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n儲東江水水塘含致癌物 疑來自內地工廠廢水　無法被濾水器濾走分解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/914055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/914055</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a608c223c2de8ded3bcdcc10d6ee3a533059895","tid":914191,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"就咁嘅 水務署嘅化驗師日撚日都生啪緊啲未煲過嘅食水<br />\n你會覺得有問題? 人地花錢讀咁多書會同你玩命?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">綠色和平於今年7月抽驗5個水塘共10個淡水樣本，包括大埔船灣淡水湖、沙田城門水塘、屯門大欖涌水塘、西貢萬宜水庫以及大嶼山石壁水塘</span><br />\n未處理過嘅水就緊係人撚死你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f69a1d7ac244bf89a36ff21b0bc14a7f6e7be4","tid":914191,"uid":87281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6bc54d43404b81f3b16f17c43c58939adaa844a","tid":914191,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"一定係3m<br />\n<br />\n利申，愛國用小米"},{"pid":"e66f3cbd790cc2034d08c8ea9633b34098856c91","tid":914191,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6bc54d43404b81f3b16f17c43c58939adaa844a","tid":914191,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:58:11.000Z"